## Summary

When there is no tags configured, the assembly name is used as a tag for each operation by default (related with #55884).

## Motivation and goals

- The principal motivation is do not show the assembly name to the user.

## In scope

The major scenario is when API has no tags definition to be used on documentation.

## Risks / unknowns

Something be wrong with the open api json being generated without the operation tags.

